data.description: Step inside and experience the ultimate in spacious and comfortable living for your family located on a beautiful corner lot. Enter the spacious living room, designed for relaxation and entertainment, where you will be greeted by the warm glow of the electric fireplace. Whether you are hosting a grand feast or casual breakfast, the oversized breakfast buffet will accommodate all your needs. The lower-level family room/rec room/ bar area offers a world of entertainment possibilities completer with a vintage shuffleboard included. Storage GALORE! You can keep your space organized and clutter-free with all of the thoughtful storage areas available, allowing easy access to all of your things when you need them.
